---
title: Mint & Parsley Tabbouleh Salad with Garlic Couscous | Serves 2
description: Try our version of a Middle Eastern staple – tabbouleh! Garlic-infused couscous is a hearty addition to this parsley-flecked salad,
while the mint and squeeze of lemon juice add a delightful zing to this side dish.
